name: Lust
description:
He who gives away shall have real gain. 
He who subdues himself shall be free; 
he shall cease to be a slave of passions. 
The righteous man casts off evil, 
and by rooting out lust, bitterness, 
and illusion do we reach Nirvana.

"Lust" art is made by using a combination of
3D, 2D and vectors.
Its a 4000x4000 static image that can be also printed
in a 130cm max res hd print.
